      <title>碧桂园延长债券期限以避免首次本地违约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/country-garden-extends-bonds-to-avoid-first-local-default</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，中国开发商碧桂园控股有限公司是中国更广泛的房地产债务危机的最大象征之一，该公司获得推迟三元人民币债券付款的批准，暂时避免了首次本地违约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/country-garden-extends-bonds-to-avoid-first-local-default</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:31:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
